  <brief_title>Effects of Dietary Interventions on the Brain in Mild Cognitive Impairment (MCI)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Enhancing Memory Functions in Patients With Mild Cognitive Impairment by Dietary Interventions and in Combination With Exercise and Cognitive Training - Proof of Concept and Mechanisms</official_title>
